00:09:36.815 --> 00:09:39.542
Was there any folder for Jang Jin Soo?

00:09:39.542 --> 00:09:42.496
I didn't see anything about Jang Jin Soo's trial records,

00:09:42.496 --> 00:09:45.901
but it seems like he paid special attention to Team Leader Nam.

00:09:45.901 --> 00:09:48.210
He saved everything from his identification record,

00:09:48.210 --> 00:09:52.517
his past case files, and what he has been up to currently.

00:09:52.517 --> 00:09:53.993
But why? Why?

00:09:53.993 --> 00:09:57.817
Why is Yoo Jeong Seok interested in Nam Gook Hyeon?

