Mom told me that I shouldn't leave you alone to do whatever you want.

00:42:51.169 --> 00:42:53.781
She said you think you're always right

00:42:53.781 --> 00:42:57.165
and that you listened to me, so I should keep following you and nagging at you.

00:42:57.165 --> 00:42:59.037
Hey, that's─

