That's when I used to run student protests.

00:43:02.954 --> 00:43:06.969
Now I'm in a position to take care of you.

00:43:06.969 --> 00:43:08.949
You're right.

00:43:09.861 --> 00:43:12.527
You don't need me by your side.

00:43:12.527 --> 00:43:16.573
You've already become a great person.

00:43:17.423 --> 00:43:18.672
Jeong Seok, are you─

00:43:18.672 --> 00:43:20.296
Hyeong.

00:43:20.296 --> 00:43:22.047
Do you trust me?

00:43:22.689 --> 00:43:26.901
You know, I always have a plan.

