Hey, how could you joke at a time like this?

00:43:32.116 --> 00:43:34.149
I haven't finished drafting the plan yet.

00:43:34.149 --> 00:43:36.805
I'll brief you on it when it's finished.

00:43:36.805 --> 00:43:39.929
I'm sure you'll agree with it.

00:43:39.929 --> 00:43:41.899
- Are you sure you're all right?
- Of course.

00:43:41.899 --> 00:43:44.396
I can trust you, right?

00:43:44.396 --> 00:43:46.592
When this is all done,

00:43:46.592 --> 00:43:49.611
I might be looking down at you from way above.

00:43:49.611 --> 00:43:51.468
You better brace yourself.

00:43:53.196 --> 00:43:56.077
Okay. Make sure that happens.

00:43:56.077 --> 00:44:01.682
Let's do a special toast for me today.

00:44:03.228 --> 00:44:06.194
Everything will work out, Yoo Jeong Seok.

00:44:12.054 --> 00:44:17.158
Ma'am, my little brother loves spicy pork.

00:44:17.158 --> 00:44:18.560
Can you give us one more plate of it, please?

00:44:18.560 --> 00:44:20.430
Sure.

