I'm saying that it's good!

00:56:02.802 --> 00:56:05.893
It won't do any good to have my name on there.

00:56:05.893 --> 00:56:11.572
Anyway, the idiots from Team 2 finally did it!

00:56:14.238 --> 00:56:21.210
Five years ago, I killed Jo Seong Gi, a dirty cop, and Detective Jang Jin Soo from the West Police Department.

00:56:21.210 --> 00:56:24.911
This is my confession and the last article that I'm writing as a Jeonghan Daily journalist

00:56:24.911 --> 00:56:28.961
in order to tell the truth to the readers."

00:56:28.961 --> 00:56:32.144
"I contemplated turning myself in to the police,

00:56:32.144 --> 00:56:37.387
but the police had already settled on Lee Dae Cheol as the one who killed Detective Jang Jin Soo,

