"I'm the one who killed Lee Dae Cheol."

00:57:33.485 --> 00:57:37.109
[Deceased: Lee Dae Cheol]

00:57:52.205 --> 00:57:54.005
Yes, Senior Manager Yoo.

00:57:54.875 --> 00:57:57.142
How am I supposed to take this?

00:57:57.142 --> 00:58:00.492
Do you remember the present I have for you?

00:58:00.492 --> 00:58:04.286
Oh, that present was my ticket to hell?

00:58:04.286 --> 00:58:08.079
No, I haven't given you the present yet.

00:58:08.079 --> 00:58:11.894
Let's meet. I'll give it to you in person.

00:58:11.894 --> 00:58:14.406
What more could possibly be left?

00:58:14.406 --> 00:58:18.192
Do you know that Jo Seong Dae, the man you ordered to commit murder,

00:58:18.192 --> 00:58:22.102
was the brother of Jo Seong Gi, the man I killed?

00:58:22.102 --> 00:58:26.836
Jo Seong Dae blackmailed me after finding out that I had killed his brother.

00:58:26.836 --> 00:58:29.370
And I have that audio recording.

00:58:30.032 --> 00:58:31.698
How will that help me?

