It can suggest that I'm the one who had ordered Jo Seong Dae

00:58:35.668 --> 00:58:40.307
to kill Park Geon Ho in order to bury Lee Dae Cheol's case, not you.

00:58:40.875 --> 00:58:45.508
Why... would you give that recording to me?

