My sentence won't change much by adding conspiracy to murder.

00:58:58.141 --> 00:58:59.741
Okay.

00:58:59.741 --> 00:59:02.093
I'll take a listen before I make my decision.

00:59:02.117 --> 00:59:05.700
Where can I find that present?

