Ask the police. Why are you asking us?

00:59:16.330 --> 00:59:19.200
Yes.

00:59:19.203 --> 00:59:20.903
Hello?

00:59:20.903 --> 00:59:23.958
I've confirmed the facts for my article.

00:59:23.958 --> 00:59:25.324
Yes.

00:59:25.324 --> 00:59:27.711
I'll take responsibility for my article.

00:59:27.711 --> 00:59:29.311
Yes.

00:59:35.938 --> 00:59:36.953
Hey, Senior Manager.

00:59:36.953 --> 00:59:39.765
Jin Seo Kyeong, can you call the police for me?

00:59:39.765 --> 00:59:41.028
What's this about?

00:59:41.028 --> 00:59:43.462
I'm going to meet Oh Jong Tae, but something doesn't feel right.

00:59:43.462 --> 00:59:45.626
Ask the police to protect me.

00:59:45.626 --> 00:59:47.429
Why? What is Oh Jong Tae going to do?

00:59:47.429 --> 00:59:51.289
I've sent you the address of where we'll be meeting. Send the detectives there.

00:59:51.289 --> 00:59:54.414
Why would you meet him if it doesn't feel right?

00:59:54.414 --> 00:59:57.465
I have to take care of Oh Jong Tae.

00:59:57.465 --> 00:59:59.852
Why do you have to take care of him?

00:59:59.852 --> 01:00:03.188
Oh Jong Tae and I both pushed Lee Dae Cheol to the execution noose.

01:00:03.188 --> 01:00:06.123
I need to make Oh Jong Tae admit it.

01:00:06.123 --> 01:00:07.932
That's the last thing I have left to do.

01:00:07.932 --> 01:00:10.125
That's something the police should do.

01:00:10.125 --> 01:00:11.891
Don't put yourself in danger.

01:00:11.891 --> 01:00:14.343
My phone is running out of battery.

01:00:14.343 --> 01:00:16.634
- I'll talk to you later.
- Senior Manager!

01:00:34.506 --> 01:00:37.406
Detective Oh, you got the address I sent you, right?

01:00:37.406 --> 01:00:39.239
Please go there right now.

